docs.text: Developers This page is solely dedicated to people who are interested in understanding how this project works, rather than just whether it works or not. Firstly , I would like to thank you. Thank you for being interested in this project that I had visioned due to my own issues with Hack Club's Nest and knowint just how overwhelming it can be to someone new.
